Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是座充滿危險與機遇的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人稱「迷宮都市」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:11.48,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,在本身就如迷宮一般的街道裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.93,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,年輕人們也冒著生命危險活躍其中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我名為尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是經驗充沛的冒險者小隊「武藝百般」的輕戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,託我女朋友的福  生活一帆風順的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.96,0:00:28.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,目標是讓「武藝百般」升上A級
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:31.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克  你不能再待在我們的小隊裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:36.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我如父親般仰慕的阿爾卡斯把我踢出了小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那  分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我的…單方面認為的女朋友也背叛並拋棄了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,回過神來才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.41,renleiyongzhe text（）,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1171,992)}偶  像  宅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:49.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我已經變成狂熱的吟遊詩人愛好者了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:34.50,renleiyongzhe note1,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)\pos(690.8,841.6)}不相信人類的冒險者們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那麼  下一首曲子自然是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:41.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「聖女應援曲」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.01,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊  阿爾卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:03:00.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你要原諒為了女人而挪用資金的加洛斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這不只是關於加洛斯的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你的想法不是冒險者該有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:10.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我把你帶進隊伍培養的時候你還是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.49,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,什麼時候變得這麼巧舌如簧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.18,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你想說什…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們的對話就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我和你的作風不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.37,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你已經不再是個孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,自己去找個適合的歸屬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,阿爾卡斯  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:37.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我明明很尊敬你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:40.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你渾身濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,怎麼把人當作野狗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.17,renleiyongzhe text（）,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,992)}偶  像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:09.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我  我在做吟遊詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,完全沒見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然我才剛出道  但會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不  我指你說的吟遊詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:22.45,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,吟遊詩人的工作就是讓人打起精神鼓起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,明天我會在南門公會大廳演出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不  我不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,絕對要來哦  野狗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:35.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,明明說了不會去的
