Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.21,renleiyongzhe note 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(19.6,61.2)}粉絲感謝祭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,阿加…特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:44.57,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,來了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.90,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小阿加特真的是太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:05.28,image 2,,0,0,0,,{\p1\alpha30\fscx1200\fscy1200\pos(1344,820.8)}m -54 -24 l -54 -24 l -54 -48 l -93 -48 l -93 -48 l -93 -24 l -93 -24
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:05.28,note 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(230.4,144)}新手冒險家公會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:05.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好  在冒險者相聚的地方尋找同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,作為吟遊詩人愛好者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,花在吟遊詩人身上的錢就要踏實工作賺回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.05,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,等著我  小阿加特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:30.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,嗨…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:36.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克  你不適合當冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要是能報出「武藝百般」的名號的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要跟老朽組隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:46.85,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我已經無法相信任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.77,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,期待下次的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,沒能夠向任何人搭話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,今天跟大家一起吃的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我永遠都不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.25,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,慶祝新小隊組成  乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:13.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我大概再也不能像那樣笑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.07,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,三位新來的客人有請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.14,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.66,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,需要拼下桌真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:26.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大家和睦相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,一份燉鼴鼠豬內臟  好的馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,小隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:51.71,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,喲  小姐姐要一起冒險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.44,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,失  失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:06:59.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那塊寶石  好像有些年頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:01.96,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看起來相當值錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,而且全身上下都透出良好的教養
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,一定是被細心撫養長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:14.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但  這種人為什麼來這種小店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:17.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然看打扮像是個魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這個女人  其實是刺客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:26.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,神官則是四處買醉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,和兩旁的女孩子一起來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:29.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:31.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,剛從夜總會出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,化妝品的味道很明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:38.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,關鍵的銘牌也沒有  是被革職了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:43.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,面對神官這種有人氣的職業也沒人來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:46.33,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,龍人族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.15,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有身經百戰的勇者的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但她簡直是負傷而逃的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,為阿爾卡斯乾杯  也為可愛的女友乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.37,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,眼前這些陰沉的傢伙也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.96,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,什麼冒險者啊  什麼戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,反正同伴總有一日會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,和身邊的人互相信任簡直是痴人說夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.42,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,阿爾卡斯說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.78,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我說不定不適合當冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:31.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人類這東西根本不值得相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雷光擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:08.20,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不愧是艾蕾納菲爾特家的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,水屬性和風屬性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.37,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,都掌握得爐火純青才能有這般水平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,學魔法不是為了出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:17.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,而是為了自己的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真是精彩  緹婭娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:24.78,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,如此得心應手地使用複合屬性還不失謙遜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.64,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你正是我校的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,多謝誇獎  師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:38.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,魔法的目的不只是讓生活更加便利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,學習魔法就是學習人類社會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:46.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,也就是學習這個世界的構成本身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:05.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,沒關係  給我來杯紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:15.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是緹婭娜啊  今天氣色不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,就是啊  聽我說亞歷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:22.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,又用精彩的魔法驚艷了老師們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,師傅大大讚賞了我的雷魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,可以提前一年畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,啊  那可真是厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  和傳聞中一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這位是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是迪爾科特家的長女  莉蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.65,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哦  是那位做商人的暴發戶家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.01,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,別用這種方式說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,聽說在學校你也是這樣跟她找茬的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:54.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,緹婭娜  我知道你想陷害莉蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:56.20,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:58.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,還勾引學校的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:03.52,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你剛剛侮辱的不只是我  還有整個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.17,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有傳言說老師們涉嫌收取賄賂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,從而暗箱操作學生的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:10.83,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這麼荒謬的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,到此為止吧  緹婭娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:14.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,亞  亞歷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:16.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,賣弄自己擅長的魔法也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,倚仗權勢投來的憐憫的眼神也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你總是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.29,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,「我是為了你啊  亞歷克斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,為了我而努力  哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:30.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你知道你成為第一後我被多少人在暗地裡嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我被期待能成為魔法師團的父親的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:37.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,被未婚妻超越的可憐男人在背地裡有多大的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,亞歷克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,和你的婚約  以及至今為止我受辱的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:51.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,緹婭娜  你究竟在看著誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你究竟在看著誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.66,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你在眼前看到的又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:43.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,也許我看到的只是我自己而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們不雇沒有介紹信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,貴族的大小姐在我們這可待不久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊  我們這不缺人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,工作也不好找啊
