Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,快…快…快…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.78,renleiyongzhe text up,,0,0,0,,上啊  你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,快…快…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:40.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,贏錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.72,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這就是賭博可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:48.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不出例外  不久之後我就經歷了賭博的洗禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:52.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,輸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,房租怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.32,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,{\p1\fscx1200\fscy1200\alpha50\pos(480,737.6)}m 0 0 l 0 -31 l -27 -31 l -27 0
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.32,note 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(148.8,292.8)}來吧\N冒險者\N  {\c&H9870F1&}性別不限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.57,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你是魔法師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,啊不  沒事  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.98,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不行  得有笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:18.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有怪物  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:26.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,三位新來的客人有請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,需要拼下桌真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:30.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,大家和睦相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.90,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,一份燉鼴鼠豬內臟  好的馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你被戀人給…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那確實夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你好意思這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,喔  在吐槽我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,神官大人你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:52.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我居住的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,有著信仰天啟神梅德拉的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.02,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,同時也盛產藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,而我也是其中一名神官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.63,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,傑姆大人  傑姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,今天我找到苧麻了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.37,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  米莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.68,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是藥草錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,下次見了  傑姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,傑姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:36.54,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你好呀  米莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.11,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,今天很晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,為了傑姆大人我有好好努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.08,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,傑姆大人  你喜歡米莉爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,今天這麼愛撒嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,才不是  我也是個大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我想變得更加成熟一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  米莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:06.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是一名神官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.22,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我不能跟他人有所交往
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你也應該為了你自己而努力才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,傑姆大人你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:35.36,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這都是傑姆大人你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.71,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,非常感謝您  傑姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:41.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,您言重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,還有就是  恭喜您啊傑姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:50.10,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,聽說您要升高級神官了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,像我這樣的小年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,奇怪的傳聞倒是四處飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,讓開路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,傑姆在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:00.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,米莉爾  發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:06.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:08.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,哼  還在演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.24,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你不是還給了她錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,米…米莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:20.04,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我明明是那麼相信傑姆大人你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.35,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,米莉爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,就你還挑起食來了啊  神官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,三個月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:39.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,三個月後我遭到放逐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:43.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,沒人相信我是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:46.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,給我滾出去  你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我信了你真是瞎了眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.53,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是神官大人呀  歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:06.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,您正在巡禮什麼的途中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.00,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.13,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.39,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我幫你治一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.13,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,睡得舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.01,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,多虧了您我的腰完全沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,已經好了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,千萬不要勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:01.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,慢性腰疼需要時間去調理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:05.89,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那你得再多待一陣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:07.92,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:12.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你去迷宮都市做個冒險者比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.47,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,結識同伴  與異性墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.30,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,偶爾縱樂一下也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:23.14,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要去看看還未見識過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.19,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你並沒有什麼罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:28.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.16,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但是  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,對了  我想起有點好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.95,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這些我不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:47.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那就當布施了  神官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然是「原」神官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是之前的白痴用來付賒的賬留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:58.69,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你要活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:00.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.97,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,然後就只記住了跟女人玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:05.64,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,光顧著花天酒地是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:07.64,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,雖然你說得不太好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,但簡單來說是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,男人是不是都這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:21.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,反正你們的事我也不會全信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,說到底不過是酒桌上的泛泛而談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.41,0:20:27.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,萍水相逢之人當晚閒扯的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你們也跟我一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:32.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:37.40,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,其實我接下來打算去打倒魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:40.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:42.34,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是不是該到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我這邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:56.23,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我重要的東西被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.79,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,被我最重要的人所奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:01.27,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.84,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這個不能拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.07,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,喝醉發酒瘋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.75,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,是是  我有在聽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,所以說  我就跟他說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.90,0:21:15.55,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.60,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你真的是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.01,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.51,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.59,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.68,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,糾纏不清的男人惹人嫌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.70,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克  你真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.68,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,最棒的ATM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:37.80,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,等等  庫洛妮爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.85,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,告訴我這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.09,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這群人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:55.94,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我已經吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:02.21,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,人類這東西根本不值得相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:07.41,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,那麼  你們是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:08.58,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,趕緊給我出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:09.81,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,然後這裡是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.38,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我是魔法師緹婭娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:14.26,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這裡是我寶貴的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.06,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,要離開的話麻煩那邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:19.03,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.88,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這是我一生的失策
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:21.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.09,0:22:33.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我  我在做吟遊詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.57,0:22:37.49,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:41.31,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:42.73,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,這樣下去就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:44.28,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,尼克先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:46.50,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們就這麼散了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:48.74,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,之後還能維持生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:55.67,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,做吟遊詩人愛好者  盡享美食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:22:57.87,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,亦或是在賭博和女人身上撒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:01.15,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,在這種吃了上頓愁下頓的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:04.12,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,隨時都可能無法再做自己喜歡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:05.43,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真的行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:07.82,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,讓這樣的悲慘生活一直持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:08.99,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,真的甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.86,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,我們的喜好到此為止真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:15.61,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:17.46,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:20.57,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,誰也不相信的我們四個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.56,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,來組隊冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.05,0:23:29.91,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,好的  這群人有朝一日將會拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:33.76,renleiyongzhe text,,0,0,0,,不過那也是很久很久之後的事情了
